      "1.46 million Chinese official-news articles, aggregated to article level, linked to Chinese government bond excess returns; the sample period is not stated.",
      "An unnamed large language model performs semantic annotation to build the Official Monetary Policy Action Score; the paper reports no accuracy or agreement check against ground truth.",
      "The resulting Policy Action Signal predicts bond excess returns beyond yield-curve factors, with stronger effects on long-maturity bonds, and its persistent component forecasts lower future yields."
